{% set description %}
  Code Snippet displays a block of syntax-highlighted code with support for several programming languages. See schema for all language options.
{% endset %}

{% set notes %}
  <bolt-ol>
    <bolt-li>The component is only intended for code blocks. If you need to display code inline, simply use the HTML <code>{{ '<code>'|e }}</code> element.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li>Use Twig whenver possible, but if you must use HTML, be sure to do the following to work with standard HTML behaviors:
      <bolt-ol>
        <bolt-li>Trim leading and trailing whitespace inside the <code>{{ '<code>'|e }}</code> element to rid of any undesired indents or whitespace.</bolt-li>
        <bolt-li>Certain special characters (such as &lt; and &gt;) must be converted to HTML entities.</bolt-li>
      </bolt-ol>
    </bolt-li>
  </bolt-ol>
{% endset %}

{% set demo %}
{% set code_snippet %}
<h1>Hello world!</h1>
<p>This is a code snippet.</p>
{% endset %}
{% include '@bolt-components-code-snippet/code-snippet.twig' with {
  content: code_snippet,
  lang: 'html',
} only %}
{% endset %}

{% set twig_markup %}
{% verbatim %}
{% set code_snippet %}
<h1>Hello world!</h1>
<p>This is a code snippet.</p>
{% endset %}

{% include '@bolt-components-code-snippet/code-snippet.twig' with {
  content: code_snippet,
  lang: 'html',
} only %}
{% endverbatim %}
{% endset %}

{% set html_markup %}
<div class="c-bolt-code-snippet c-bolt-code-snippet--light" data-bolt-lang="html">
<pre><code>&lt;h1&gt;Hello world!&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a code snippet.&lt;/p&gt;</code></pre>
</div>
{% endset %}

{% include '@utils/pattern-doc-page.twig' with {
  title: 'Basic Code Snippet',
  description: description,
  notes: notes,
  demo: demo,
  twig_markup: twig_markup,
  html_markup: html_markup
} only %}
